      </h1>
      <p>The first "classless" Tailwind CSS framework.</p>
    </hgroup>

    <button><DownloadIcon customClasses='mr-2' /> Download</button>
  </section>

  <section class='w-full py-20 space-y-4 text-sm'>
    <div class='overflow-x-scroll flex gap-2 items-start'>
      <span class='element-tag'>accordion</span>
      <span class='element-tag'>body</span>
      <span class='element-tag'>button</span>
