      <span class='element-tag'>a</span>
      <span class='element-tag'>ol</span>
      <span class='element-tag'>ul</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class='section'>
    <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 grid-rows-4 gap-3 w-full'>
      <div class='md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 bento-card'>
        <h2>Accordion</h2>

        <details>
          <summary>What is this?</summary>
          <p>
            This is a "classless" css library built on top of Tailwind CSS that
            you download and copy/paste to your project that gives you a great
            place to start your design system.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details>
          <summary>When would I use this?</summary>
          <p>
            Use this on your personal projects to your enterprise applications.
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
      <div class='md:col-span-2 md:row-span-1 bento-card'>
        <h2>Button</h2>

        <div class='flex flex-col gap-2'>
          <button>Hi ðŸ‘‹!</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='md:col-span-2 md:row-span-1 bento-card'>
        <h2>Checkbox</h2>

        <label>
          <input type='checkbox' name='language' checked />
          English
        </label>

        <label>
          <input type='checkbox' name='language' />
          German
        </label>
        <label>
          <input type='checkbox' name='language' />
          Spanish
        </label>
      </div>
      <div class='md:col-span-1 md:row-span-2 bento-card'>
        <h2>Dropdown</h2>
        <details class='dropdown'>
          <summary>Open Me!</summary>
          <ul>
            <li tabindex='1'><a>Item 1</a></li>
            <li tabindex='1'><a>Item 2</a></li>
          </ul>
        </details>
      </div>
      <div class='md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 bento-card'>
        <h2>Inputs</h2>

        <div class='flex flex-col gap-2'>
          <label>
            Email
            <input type='text' class='grow' placeholder='daisy@site.com' />
          </label>

          <label>
            <svg
              xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
              fill='none'
              viewBox='0 0 24 24'
              stroke-width='1.5'
              stroke='currentColor'
              class='w-6 h-6'>
              <path
                stroke-linecap='round'
                stroke-linejoin='round'
                d='M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632Z'
              ></path>
            </svg>
            <input type='text' class='grow' placeholder='username' />
          </label>

          <input type='date' name='date' aria-label='Date' />

          <div class='self-stretch'>
            <input
              type='text'
              name='invalid'
              value='Invalid'
              aria-invalid='true'
              class='w-full'
            />
            <small>This is an error message.</small>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='md:col-span-1 md:row-span-2 bento-card'>
        <h2>Switch</h2>
        <label>
          <input type='checkbox' role='switch' />
          On/Off
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class='section py-12'>
    <hgroup>
      <h2>Tired of writing a <b>TON</b> of classnames?</h2>
      <p>For every element, every page, every project, again and againâ€¦</p>
    </hgroup>

    <div>
      <h3>Before</h3>
      <Code
        lang='html'
        code=`
<button class="h-9 min-h-9 inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded text-sm font-normal transition-colors px-4 py-2 cursor-pointer border-transparent border bg-surface-950 text-foreground-50 duration-150 hover:bg-opacity-90">Hi ðŸ‘‹!</button>
`
        customClasses='px-4 py-6 overflow-x-hidden text-wrap'
      />

      <h3>After</h3>
      <Code
        lang='html'
        code=`
<button>Hi ðŸ‘‹!</button>
`
        customClasses='px-4 py-6 overflow-x-hidden text-wrap'
      />

      <h3>Result</h3>

      <button>Hi ðŸ‘‹!</button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- benefits -->

  <section></section>

  <!-- 
26+ components

**Effortless Integration, Maximum Impact**
- *Seamless Tailwind CSS Integration*: Our library is built on the principles of Tailwind CSS, ensuring that you can integrate it effortlessly into your existing projects without any compatibility concerns.

**Design Consistency, Uncompromised Flexibility**
- *Native HTML Element Styling*: Enjoy consistent, beautiful styles out of the box for all native HTML elements, or take full control to customize the styles to fit your unique brand identity.

**Developer-Friendly, Community-Driven**
- *Open Source Collaboration*: As an open source library, we encourage and support community contributions, making our CSS library constantly evolve with the needs and innovations of developers like you.

**Lightweight Code, Heavyweight Performance**
- *Optimized for Speed*: Our CSS library is designed to be lightweight, ensuring that your website loads quickly, providing a better user experience and improving SEO rankings.

**Future-Proof Your Project**
- *Regular Updates and Improvements*: With a commitment to staying up-to-date with the latest web standards, our library ensures that your project remains at the forefront of web design trends and best practices.

 -->
</BaseLayout>

